    <string name="pdf_title">Tayanch — Capstone Assignment</string>
    <string name="pdf_body">Goal: demonstrate you can apply this level\'s skills on a real project.\n\nDeliverables:\n  1. A GitHub repository implementing the brief below.\n  2. A short README explaining your design and security trade-offs.\n\nBrief:\n  Build and harden a small login API. Implement Argon2id password hashing,\n  JWT access + rotating refresh tokens, strict rate limiting on the auth\n  routes, and parameterised database queries. Document the threats each\n  control mitigates.\n\nWhen done: open the Tayanch app -> Career -> Assignments, and paste your\n  GitHub repo link to submit it for evaluator review.</string>
